        <Parent_String>cannons (artillery) [300036936], artillery by form [300222657], artillery (firearms) [300036931], firearms [300037148], projectile weapons with explosive propellant [300208782], projectile weapons [300203727], armaments [300420324], weapons [300036926], Weapons and Ammunition (hierarchy name) [300036743], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
